      <br>
      <div class="panel panel-default">
        <div class="panel-heading">
          <h3 class="panel-title">License</h3>
          <div>Each open source repo must have an open source license agreed to by your business and legal team.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      -->
    </div>
  </div>
</div>